c: 2
v: 93
t: "And (remember) when, We took your Promise and We raised above you Mount (Sinai, saying): \"Hold firmly to what We have given you, and obey:\" They said: \"We hear, and we disobey:\" And they had to take into their hearts the worship of the calf because they have no Faith. Say: \"The commands of your Faith are truly not enough— If you have any faith"